---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <video autoplay loop muted playsinline width="100%">
    <source src="/img/sprinkler.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    Your browser does not support the video tag.
  </video>

  <div class="about-content">
    <div>
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Creating beautiful outdoor spaces is more than just a jo, it’s a
        passion. With years of experience in lawn care, landscape design, and
        sustainable practices, our team is dedicated to helping homeowners and
        businesses transform their properties into vibrant, welcoming
        environments.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>Our Philosophy</h3>
      <p>
        We believe that a well-maintained lawn is the foundation of a great
        landscape. Whether it's a cozy backyard retreat or a polished commercial
        frontage, every project is approached with care, creativity, and
        attention to detail.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>What We Offer</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Custom Landscape Design</strong>: Tailored layouts that
          reflect your style and maximize your space.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Routine Lawn Maintenance</strong>: Reliable mowing, edging,
          fertilization, and seasonal care.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Eco-Friendly Solutions</strong>: Native plants, water-wise
          irrigation, and organic treatments.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Hardscaping & Enhancements</strong>: Patios, walkways,
          lighting, and more to elevate your outdoor experience.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>Why It Matters</h3>
      <p>
        A thoughtfully landscaped property doesn’t just look good—it feels good.
        It boosts curb appeal, supports local ecosystems, and creates a space
        where people want to gather, relax, and enjoy life outdoors.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  div {
    background-color: var(--accent-2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--neutral-4);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .about-content {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  h2,
  h3 {
    color: var(--primary-1);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  p {
    text-indent: 10px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
</style>
